    "user_id": "470033a5-ab5b-4579-b75b-48125082afe5",
    "rating": 5,
    "content": "The variety of dishes is amazing - very hard to make a decision on what you want to order, so you might want to come back more often!\nI had a bowl with \"beef\", fresh vegetables, rice and a fried dumpling and it was one of the best vegan eat outs I ever had.",
