    "video_url": null,
    "engagement_score": 0
  },
  {
    "id": "47686d8c-e492-4291-946b-0103b3f987a9",
    "place_id": "e937b6cf-189b-4681-8a8c-f1c8dba4a482",
    "user_id": "39d689ba-50f5-4305-b57d-2ae1f6fd5daa",
    "rating": 4,
    "content": "You can taste here delicious vegan desserts and drink a delicious latte. It is better to book a table in advance, especially on weekends. The only thing that worries me is whether the cats are really comfortable in such an environment. Although it seemed to me that all the necessary conditions were created for them. The inside is clean, but don't expect any fancy place, because it is still worth considering that this is the establishment where cats live permanently.",
